      <hedline>
        <hl1>How to Give Away $21.8 Billion</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Larry Cohen letter on cover photo accompanying Jean Strouse's April 16 article holds billionaire Bill Gates apparently cannot afford decent razor (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>For a man worth almost 12 figures, you'd think Bill Gates could afford a decent razor. What's with the cheesy chin stubble on your cover?</p>
        <p>Larry Cohen  Los Angeles</p>
      </block>
